DESCRIPTION

This file contains the installation instructions for the MPEG2 StreamIt codec.
  
INSTALL

1. Make sure your StreamIt compile environment is setup correctly.
If the StreamIt environment is not yet setup, go to the StreamIt website
[http://cag.csail.mit.edu/streamit/shtml/download.shtml] and follow the 
download and setup instructions.

2. Unzip and untar the mpeg_streamit_codec.tar.gz file.
 
3. Follow the instructions in MPEG2 for running the encoder or decoder in
its various modes, or DCT_IEEE for testing the DCT by itself.
